{
  "stem": "888.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they marched us, you know, to the train, which was quite a considerable march, you know-- I would say at least about four, five kilometers.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was me, my brother, my mother, and, and all the rest of the children.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then of course, all the other people who, who were, you know, selected at that particular day to leave.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well-- well, they, you know, they walked us in the middle of the streets.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They walked us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course, you could realize, you know, how we felt-- you know, taken from your homes, and, well.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And they walked us-- as I remember, it was a sunny day.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they walked us to the train.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they loaded us in these carts, you know, the--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Railway cars.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they, they, they took us, you know, towards Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was a small child.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Didn't realize what and when.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course, you know, like for instance in each car there was maybe 40, 50 people, or maybe even more-- you know, children and elderly people and, you know--",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We-- I mean, they didn't try to separate no families at that particular time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, and they kind of herded us, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, while we were walking through the town, they weren't trying to be rough, you know?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But then, of course, you know, they were forceful.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, they were forceful.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And you know, get in, get in, get in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean, I mean, it's kind of fading after 50 years or so, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It's-- It's-- you know, I mean, it's not quite as, you know--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't-- well, they probably-- I don't recall.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
